title: Led Zeppelin - 1970 Live in Vancouver [M~u~D~S~L~i~D~e]
description:

Vancouver, Canada

Maxell Type II (5th gen)>Wavelab>Cd-R>Easy CD Creator 5 Wavs>Flac

1. Heartbreaker
2. Thank You
3. What Is & What Should Never Be
4. Communication Breakdown
5. We're Gonna Groove
6. Since I've Been Loving You
7. Whole Lotta Love

Background:
Originally a Canadian FM broadcast, this show circulated under the extremely rare bootleg Lp "Pure Blues". It resurfaced reissued as "Mudslide", but in poorer quality than the original. This source is from a copy of the original broadcast and not from any of the bootleg Lps.
